{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "b1a7e9c2-3d4f-4a6b-9c8d-stocks-backend01",
    "name": "Stocks Backend",
    "description": "Colección completa del backend (Node + Express + PostgreSQL + JWT + FCM + price hub).\n\n- `{{baseUrl}}` por defecto `http://localhost:3000`.\n- **Auth** guarda el JWT en `{{token}}` automáticamente (test script en Register/Login).\n- **Create alert** guarda el id en `{{webhookId}}` automáticamente.\n- El endpoint en tiempo real es un **WebSocket**: `{{wsUrl}}` (`ws://localhost:3000/ws`). Ver la carpeta _Real-time (WebSocket)_.\n\nOrden sugerido: Register → Login → Register device → Create alert → (Test push / List / Get / Delete).",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }]
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:3000", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "wsUrl", "value": "ws://localhost:3000/ws", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "userEmail", "value": "me@test.com", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "userPassword", "value": "secret1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "fcmToken", "value": "test-fcm-token-123", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "symbol", "value": "AAPL", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "webhookId", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "request": {
        "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/health",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["health"]
        },
        "description": "Estado del servicio y de las integraciones: `{ status, fcm, finnhub, streaming }`."
      },
      "response": []
    },
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('status is 201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.token) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.token);",
                  "  console.log('token saved');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{userEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{userPassword}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "register"]
            },
            "description": "Crea un usuario y devuelve `{ token, user }`. Guarda el token en `{{token}}`."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('status is 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.token) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.token);",
                  "  console.log('token saved');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{userEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{userPassword}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Inicia sesión y devuelve `{ token, user }`. Guarda el token en `{{token}}`."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Me",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/me",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "me"]
            },
            "description": "Devuelve el usuario del Bearer token. Requiere `{{token}}` (heredado de la colección)."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Devices",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register device (FCM token)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"token\": \"{{fcmToken}}\",\n  \"platform\": \"android\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/devices",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["devices"]
            },
            "description": "Registra (upsert) el token FCM del dispositivo. Auth opcional: si mandas el Bearer, ata el device al usuario.\n\nRespuesta: `{ id, token, platform, active, createdAt }`."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Webhooks (Alerts)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create alert",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('status is 201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.id) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('webhookId', json.id);",
                  "  console.log('webhookId saved:', json.id);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"event\": \"stock-price-alert:{{symbol}}:above:150\",\n  \"url\": \"\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/webhooks",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["webhooks"]
            },
            "description": "Crea una alerta de precio. El `event` se codifica como `stock-price-alert:<SYMBOL>:<above|below>:<targetPrice>`.\n\nGuarda el id en `{{webhookId}}`. Respuesta: `{ id, url, event, active, createdAt }`."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "List alerts",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/webhooks",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["webhooks"]
            },
            "description": "Lista las alertas (las del usuario autenticado + anónimas)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get alert by id",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/webhooks/{{webhookId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["webhooks", "{{webhookId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Devuelve una alerta por id. Usa `{{webhookId}}` (lo setea Create alert)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Test push",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/webhooks/{{webhookId}}/test",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["webhooks", "{{webhookId}}", "test"]
            },
            "description": "Dispara un push de prueba (sin esperar al mercado) a todos los devices activos. Requiere FCM configurado para que llegue de verdad."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete alert",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/webhooks/{{webhookId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["webhooks", "{{webhookId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Elimina una alerta por id (204). También la quita del hub en tiempo real."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Real-time (WebSocket)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Stream prices  (ws://.../ws)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{wsUrl}}",
              "protocol": "ws",
              "host": ["localhost"],
              "port": "3000",
              "path": ["ws"]
            },
            "description": "Endpoint de precios en tiempo real (WebSocket).\n\nEn Postman: New → WebSocket Request → URL `{{wsUrl}}` (`ws://localhost:3000/ws`) → Connect.\n\nMensajes a enviar (cliente → servidor). `throttleMs` es opcional, por-cliente, clamp 100–10000 ms:\n\n```\n{ \"type\": \"subscribe\", \"symbols\": [\"AAPL\", \"BINANCE:BTCUSDT\"], \"throttleMs\": 1000 }\n{ \"type\": \"unsubscribe\", \"symbols\": [\"AAPL\"] }\n{ \"type\": \"throttle\", \"throttleMs\": 1000 }\n{ \"type\": \"ping\" }\n```\n\nMensajes que recibes (servidor → cliente): `welcome`, `snapshot`, `prices`, `throttle` (ack), `pong`.\n\nNota: necesitas `FINNHUB_API_KEY` para ticks reales. `BINANCE:BTCUSDT` transmite 24/7 (útil fuera de horario de mercado)."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
